snippet.title: Corridor Crusaders Launch Trailer [Nov. 24, 2019]
snippet.description:
The official launch trailer for Corridor Crusaders! Starting on November 24, 2019, get your friends and play for FREE on Steam!

In this action-packed arcade shooter, build the arena and then fight your opponents by calculating the bounces of your shots, manipulating the map, and dashing to safety!

Discord Server: https://discord.gg/M8UBVA2
Join the server to look for people to play with and talk to me!
